title: Empire Seed Announces Fall Savings on Echo and Stihl Chain Saws and Chain Saw Repairs and Other Outdoor Gas Powered Blowers in the Greater Temple TX Area Including Harker Heights and Killeen
text:
Local lawn care company offers savings on a full selection of outdoor power equipment
 TEMPLE-KILLEEN, TX, October 09, Empire Seed of Temple announces Fall Savings on outdoor power equipment, especially Echo and Stihl chain saws. Empire Seed sells lawncare products and equipment manufactured by most of the major brands. They also have a service department to repair and do maintenance work on everything they sell.
"We carry a wide selection of Stihl and Echo chain saws, trimmers and blowers," said Ross Gregory, Owner of Empire Seed Co. "If we do not have the exact model in stock we can get it for you quickly. Come down to our store or visit our web site. We also provide service for what we sell - we can handle all of your outdoor power equipment repairs."
Empire Seed also sells lawn mowers, lawncare products and can install lawn sprinkler systems. Also, if your irrigation system needs to be serviced, give Empire Seed a call.
Learn more about our chain saws:
http://www.empireseedturfandirrigation.com/chain-saw-repairs-temple.a ... pr-2015-10
Lawn Care Products:
http://www.empireseedturfandirrigation.com/lawn-care-products-temple. ... pr-2015-10
Lawn Mowers:
http://www.empireseedturfandirrigation.com/lawn-mowers-for-sale-templ ... pr-2015-10
About Empire Seed
Empire Seed Co. has been a family owned business in the heart of downtown Temple, Texas since 1937. Empire Seed sells and services many brands of outdoor power equipment including Scag, Honda, Gravely, Toro, Stihl, Echo and many others. We provide maintenance and repairs for most brands of small engines and we also install and provide service for water irrigation systems. In addition, we sell numerous brands of lawn care products. We service the greater Temple area including McGregor, Marlin, Gatesville, Bruceville-Eddy, Killeen, Salado, Cameron and Georgetown. "All the products and services you'll ever need to maintain your lawn or garden" - Empire Seed.
Visit our Web Site to learn more: http://www.empireseedturfandirrigation.com/index.asp?source=pr-2015-10
